"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-12-tom-daley-announces-retirement-diving-following-paris-olympics-21407605\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Team GB legend Tom Daley has announced his retirement from diving afterwinning a silver medal at this summer's Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 126, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 7, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999949632960546, \"rank\": 5.036729179801481e-06, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 24, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0327961227279259e-51, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his retirement\", \"from\": 39, \"to\": 53}, {\"ngram\": \"diving\", \"from\": 59, \"to\": 65}, {\"ngram\": \"a silver medal\", \"from\": 79, \"to\": 93}, {\"ngram\": \"this summer's Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 97, \"to\": 125}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Daley, 30, was selected as one of Team GB's flagbearers for the opening ceremony, alongside rower Helen Glover, ahead of his fifth consecutive appearance at an Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 128, \"to\": 302, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 162, \"end\": 169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999949632960546, \"rank\": 5.036729179801481e-06, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 226, \"end\": 238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Helen_Glover_(rower)\", \"score\": 0.9968858553495725, \"rank\": 0.0031234382808593376, \"text\": \"Helen Glover\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Helen_Glover_(rower)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Helen_Glover_(rower)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Daley\", \"from\": 128, \"to\": 133}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 188, \"to\": 208}, {\"ngram\": \"his fifth consecutive appearance\", \"from\": 249, \"to\": 281}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic Games\", \"from\": 285, \"to\": 301}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After making his Olympic debut aged just 14 at the Beijing Games in 2008, Daley went on to establish himself as one of the most recognisable faces in British sport.\", \"from\": 304, \"to\": 468, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 454, \"end\": 461, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.6494923694252001, \"rank\": 0.2648257560877347, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his Olympic debut\", \"from\": 317, \"to\": 334}, {\"ngram\": \"the Beijing Games\", \"from\": 351, \"to\": 368}, {\"ngram\": \"Daley\", \"from\": 378, \"to\": 383}, {\"ngram\": \"the most recognisable faces\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 450}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The silver Daley won alongside Noah Williams in the men's synchronised 10m competition was the fifth medal of his long Olympic career, after three bronzes and the gold he clinched in Tokyo three years ago.\", \"from\": 470, \"to\": 675, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 501, \"end\": 514, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"score\": 0.999998273608197, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Williams\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\"}, {\"begin\": 653, \"end\": 658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.595114614708969, \"rank\": 0.6803456282374353, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The silver\", \"from\": 470, \"to\": 480}, {\"ngram\": \"Daley\", \"from\": 481, \"to\": 486}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's synchronised 10m competition\", \"from\": 518, \"to\": 556}, {\"ngram\": \"the fifth medal\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 576}, {\"ngram\": \"his long Olympic career\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 603}, {\"ngram\": \"three bronzes\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 624}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold\", \"from\": 629, \"to\": 637}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking toBritish Vogue, Daley revealed that he had already made the decision to call it quits before adding another medal to his sizeable collection in the French capital this summer.\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 862, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 835, \"end\": 841, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9074247417019595, \"rank\": 0.10075995557315083, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"toBritish Vogue\", \"from\": 686, \"to\": 701}, {\"ngram\": \"Daley\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 708}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 743, \"to\": 755}, {\"ngram\": \"another medal\", \"from\": 787, \"to\": 800}, {\"ngram\": \"his sizeable collection\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 827}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It feels very, very surreal.\", \"from\": 864, \"to\": 893, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I felt so incredibly nervous going into this, knowing it was my last Olympics,' Daley said.\", \"from\": 894, \"to\": 985, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my last Olympics\", \"from\": 955, \"to\": 971}, {\"ngram\": \"Daley\", \"from\": 974, \"to\": 979}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'There was a lot of pressure and expectation.\", \"from\": 987, \"to\": 1032, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1003}, {\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 1007, \"to\": 1015}, {\"ngram\": \"expectation\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1031}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was eager for it to be done\\u2026 but when I walked out, and saw my husband [Dustin Lance Black] and kids [Robbie and Phoenix] and my friends and family in the audience, I was like, you know what?\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1226, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1107, \"end\": 1125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_Lance_Black\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dustin Lance Black\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_Lance_Black\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_Lance_Black\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my husband\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1105}, {\"ngram\": \"kids\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1135}, {\"ngram\": \"the audience\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1198}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is exactly why I did this.\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1258, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am here, and no matter what happens in the competition itself, I am going to be happy.'\", \"from\": 1260, \"to\": 1350, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1317}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sorry, this video is not available any more.\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1396, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this video\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1369}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After representing Great Britain for over half of his life, an 'emotional' Daley said it 'feels like the right time' to retire.\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1525, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1417, \"end\": 1430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.6645705539487544, \"rank\": 0.5041251351694779, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"over half\", \"from\": 1435, \"to\": 1444}, {\"ngram\": \"his life\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1456}, {\"ngram\": \"the right time\", \"from\": 1499, \"to\": 1513}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It was emotional at the end, up there on the platform, knowing it was going to be my last competitive dive,' he added.\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1646, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1548, \"to\": 1555}, {\"ngram\": \"the platform\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1581}, {\"ngram\": \"my last competitive dive\", \"from\": 1610, \"to\": 1634}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'But I have to make the decision at some point, and it feels like the right time.\", \"from\": 1648, \"to\": 1729, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1680}, {\"ngram\": \"some point\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1694}, {\"ngram\": \"the right time\", \"from\": 1714, \"to\": 1728}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's the right time to call it a day.'\", \"from\": 1731, \"to\": 1770, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the right time\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1751}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Daley made headlines across the world when he publicly came out as gay in December 2013 and the diver is glad to see increasingly more athletes do the same in recent years.\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1944, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Daley\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1777}, {\"ngram\": \"headlines\", \"from\": 1783, \"to\": 1792}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1809}, {\"ngram\": \"December\", \"from\": 1846, \"to\": 1854}, {\"ngram\": \"the diver\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 1873}, {\"ngram\": \"increasingly more athletes\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 1915}, {\"ngram\": \"recent years\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 1943}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'With every Olympics, there are more and more out athletes.\", \"from\": 1946, \"to\": 2005, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every Olympics\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 1966}, {\"ngram\": \"more and more out athletes\", \"from\": 1978, \"to\": 2004}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's powerful,' he continued.\", \"from\": 2006, \"to\": 2035, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I think there is a lot of pressure for when people do come out to be an activist and to be outspoken.\", \"from\": 2037, \"to\": 2139, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2060}, {\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 2064, \"to\": 2072}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2082, \"to\": 2088}, {\"ngram\": \"an activist\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2118}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And sometimes that's just not in some people's nature.\", \"from\": 2140, \"to\": 2194, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some people's nature\", \"from\": 2173, \"to\": 2193}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think this might be part of the reason why possibly more people have not felt as comfortable with coming out.\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2306, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2217, \"to\": 2221}, {\"ngram\": \"the reason\", \"from\": 2225, \"to\": 2235}, {\"ngram\": \"possibly more people\", \"from\": 2240, \"to\": 2260}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I also think that [the world of sport] is such a heteronormative space\\u2026 lots of queer kids, when they are younger, have this automatic feeling that they should not fit into sports, so they do not pursue them.\", \"from\": 2308, \"to\": 2517, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 2341, \"to\": 2346}, {\"ngram\": \"such a heteronormative space\", \"from\": 2351, \"to\": 2379}, {\"ngram\": \"lots\", \"from\": 2381, \"to\": 2385}, {\"ngram\": \"queer kids\", \"from\": 2389, \"to\": 2399}, {\"ngram\": \"this automatic feeling\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2451}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 2482, \"to\": 2488}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I hope we will see more in the future.'\", \"from\": 2518, \"to\": 2557, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 2545, \"to\": 2555}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Daley spent the second half of the Games providing punditry for Eurosport and the four-time world champion is interested in pursuing a career in front of the camera.\", \"from\": 2559, \"to\": 2724, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Daley\", \"from\": 2559, \"to\": 2564}, {\"ngram\": \"the second half\", \"from\": 2571, \"to\": 2586}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2590, \"to\": 2599}, {\"ngram\": \"punditry\", \"from\": 2610, \"to\": 2618}, {\"ngram\": \"Eurosport\", \"from\": 2623, \"to\": 2632}, {\"ngram\": \"the four-time world champion\", \"from\": 2637, \"to\": 2665}, {\"ngram\": \"a career\", \"from\": 2692, \"to\": 2700}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 2704, \"to\": 2709}, {\"ngram\": \"the camera\", \"from\": 2713, \"to\": 2723}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He went on: 'I have also enrolled in a class, a course at the Fashion Institute of Design and Merchandising (FIDM) in Los Angeles, to be able to learn how to sew.\", \"from\": 2726, \"to\": 2888, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2844, \"end\": 2855, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999999859028, \"rank\": 1.4129902918665758e-11, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a class\", \"from\": 2763, \"to\": 2770}, {\"ngram\": \"the Fashion Institute\", \"from\": 2784, \"to\": 2805}, {\"ngram\": \"Design\", \"from\": 2809, \"to\": 2815}, {\"ngram\": \"Merchandising (FIDM\", \"from\": 2820, \"to\": 2839}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I knit and I crochet, but sewing will just add a whole different level of knowledge as to how to construct things.\", \"from\": 2890, \"to\": 3005, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sewing\", \"from\": 2917, \"to\": 2923}, {\"ngram\": \"a whole different level\", \"from\": 2938, \"to\": 2961}, {\"ngram\": \"knowledge\", \"from\": 2965, \"to\": 2974}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 2998, \"to\": 3004}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I have actually designed a couple of pieces of underwear that I am going to be launching, and then I am also hoping to launch a swimwear project next year.'\", \"from\": 3007, \"to\": 3164, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a couple\", \"from\": 3033, \"to\": 3041}, {\"ngram\": \"pieces\", \"from\": 3045, \"to\": 3051}, {\"ngram\": \"underwear\", \"from\": 3055, \"to\": 3064}, {\"ngram\": \"a swimwear project\", \"from\": 3134, \"to\": 3152}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 3166, \"to\": 3214, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more stories\", \"from\": 3170, \"to\": 3182}, {\"ngram\": \"our sport page\", \"from\": 3199, \"to\": 3213}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 3216, \"to\": 3286, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Metro Sport\", \"from\": 3223, \"to\": 3234}, {\"ngram\": \"the latest news onFacebook\", \"from\": 3239, \"to\": 3265}, {\"ngram\": \"TwitterandInstagram\", \"from\": 3266, \"to\": 3285}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Team GB star Tom Daley reveals he accidentally left his silver medal behind in Paris' Olympic Village ArrowMORE:Noah Lyles' mum blasts Paris Olympics for leaving son with covid 'gasping for air' after race ArrowMORE:Most memorable and controversial moments of the Paris Olympics after a wild ride in the French capital Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 3288, \"to\": 3730, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3311, \"end\": 3320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank